'''Gamit''' is a [[language]] of India, spoken by the Gamit people of [[Tapi district]] of gujarat and by some people in surat, [[Bharuch district|Bharuch]], [[Dang District, India|Dang]] and [[Valsad district]]s of southern [[Gujarat]]. It also spoken in [[Nandurbar district|Nandurbar]] and by some people in [[Dhule district]] in northern [[Maharashtra]].
